author: Tomas Navia, Michael Learmonth
title: China Is Sending Medical Supplies Around the World So You'll Forget They Kept Coronavirus a Secret
description: For example: China sent masks to Spain by a 17-day train trip, a stunt to promote a Belt and Road infrastructure project.
content:
Now that China says that the worst of its coronavirus crisis is over, its sending billions of masks, ventilators, testing kits, and other medical supplies around the world.
